{"id":3592,"date":"2018-04-01T12:06:55","date_gmt":"2018-04-01T16:06:55","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/unitedhelp.art\/?p=3592"},"modified":"2018-04-01T12:08:59","modified_gmt":"2018-04-01T16:08:59","slug":"educational-games-for-schools-that-are-close-to-the-front-line","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/unitedhelp.art\/archives\/3592","title":{"rendered":"Educational games for schools that are close to the front line"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-3593\" src=\"http:\/\/unitedhelp.art\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/29354608_1469035513224158_1282355600266897382_o-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unitedhelp.art\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/29354608_1469035513224158_1282355600266897382_o-300x225.jpg 300w, https:\/\/unitedhelp.art\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/29354608_1469035513224158_1282355600266897382_o-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/unitedhelp.art\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/29354608_1469035513224158_1282355600266897382_o-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/unitedhelp.art\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/29354608_1469035513224158_1282355600266897382_o-285x214.jpg 285w, https:\/\/unitedhelp.art\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/29354608_1469035513224158_1282355600266897382_o.jpg 1440w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Part of the money raised at the\u00a0<a href=\"http:\/\/unitedhelp.art\/archives\/3556\">event on February 23<\/a> was collected to buy educational Ukrainian language material for schools in Donbas and Crimea. For this, we partnered with Ukrainian organization \u041d\u0435 \u0431\u0443\u0434\u044c \u0431\u0430\u0439\u0434\u0443\u0436\u0438\u043c\u200b (Don\u2019t be indifferent!)\u00a0who <a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/unitedhelp.art\/posts\/1748222105244911\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">bought\u00a0120 sets<\/a> (4,800 hrv total) of fun educational puzzle game for kids \u201c\u041c\u0430\u043d\u0434\u0440\u0456\u0432\u043aa \u0423\u043a\u0440\u0430\u0457\u043d\u043e\u044e\u201d (Ukrainian Journey). While playing the game, kids will learn many facts about their country. United Help Ukraine is happy that we had the opportunity to become a piece in a long chain involving the work of so many good people in Ukraine.<br \/>\n(The rest of the total of $475 raised for this project will be spent on educational maps for schools in the \u201cgrey zone\u201d in eastern Ukraine.)<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Part of the money raised at the\u00a0event on February 23 was collected to buy educational Ukrainian language material for schools in Donbas and Crimea. For this, we partnered with Ukrainian organization \u041d\u0435 \u0431\u0443\u0434\u044c \u0431\u0430\u0439\u0434\u0443\u0436\u0438\u043c\u200b (Don\u2019t be indifferent!)\u00a0who bought\u00a0120 sets (4,800 hrv total) of fun educational puzzle game for kids \u201c\u041c\u0430\u043d\u0434\u0440\u0456\u0432\u043aa \u0423\u043a\u0440\u0430\u0457\u043d\u043e\u044e\u201d (Ukrainian Journey). While playing<a href=\"https:\/\/unitedhelp.art\/archives\/3592\">[&#8230;]<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":18,"featured_media":3593,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[8],"tags":[70],"wppr_data":{"cwp_meta_box_check":"No"},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unitedhelp.art\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3592"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unitedhelp.art\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unitedhelp.art\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unitedhelp.art\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/18"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unitedhelp.art\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3592"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/unitedhelp.art\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3592\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3595,"href":"https:\/\/unitedhelp.